                    <span>This book is a must have! It is a whimsical read jam packed with herbal know how. Shatoiya has a wonderful outlook on life and herbalism. She effortlessly blends humour, fabulous recipes, and knowledge into one little book. I just made the chocolate cake, and it is KILLER! I have tried a few of the lotion and salve recipes and was delighted that they not only turned out, but they were so easy to make. Thank you for this wonderful treasure! It is a keeper for my own natural healing library and will be an awesome gift for many of my friends this year!</span>
                  
