                    <span>This is the best definitive book on herbs yet. Both novice and expert will find a wealth of information about the use of herbs. Having been a bookseller for many years, I have had the opportunity to view quite a few books on the subject of alternative healing and never have I found a more concise and useful book than Earth Mother Herbal. It is a good read too...full of wonderful wit, wisdom and stories.</span>
                  
              
